                    />

            
    
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">National Guard troops raided the farm two years ago.</span>
    
        <span class="attribution__credit">
        <span class="a11y">Credit: </span>
        Oklahoma National Guard
    </span>
    
    
    </figcaption>

</figure>

        
    
                    
<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="52.0">Ho had hired an Oklahoma resident, a known “straw owner” used by criminals to elude laws requiring local ownership, to pose as her majority partner, court documents say. Prosecutors charged Ho with illegal cultivation and trafficking and she was arrested at Los Angeles International Airport before she could board a flight to Hong Kong. In June of last year, Ho pleaded guilty to trafficking and received a deferred sentence to be imposed after a three-year probation period, court documents say.</p>
        
    
