    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/fields-of-green">Fields of Green</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/marijuana-oklahoma-china-immigration-safety-workers">
                                    Jiaai Zeng Died Weeks After Starting Work at an Oklahoma Marijuana Farm. His Family Wants Answers.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Thousands of Chinese immigrant laborers suffer abuse and exploitation in a U.S. marijuana underworld dominated by Chinese mafias. A human rights advocate says: “They have not escaped the darkness of China.”
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sebastian-rotella">Sebastian Rotella</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/kirsten-berg">Kirsten Berg</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Garrett Yalch</span> and <span class="name">Clifton Adcock</span>, <a href="https://www.readfrontier.org/">The Frontier</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-07-17EDT05:00">July 17, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/new-york-wage-theft-violators-government-contracts">
                <img
