                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271%27%20height%3D%271%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
                    srcset="https://img.assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/20240617-Luong-Mental-Health-Project-3834.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=105&amp;q=75&amp;w=105&amp;s=3e0587df122d1a38198f8b8221057d4d 105w, https://img.assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/20240617-Luong-Mental-Health-Project-3834.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=210&amp;q=75&amp;w=210&amp;s=f454cd50a126d5d93f06afee1d0d78f5 210w"
                    width="105"
                    height="105"
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/americas-mental-barrier">America’s Mental Barrier</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://projects.propublica.org/why-i-left-the-network/">
                                    Why It’s So Hard to Find a Therapist Who Takes Insurance
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Those who need therapy often have to pay out of pocket or go without care, even if they have health insurance. Hundreds of mental health providers told us they fled networks because insurers made their jobs impossible and their lives miserable.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/annie-waldman">Annie Waldman</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/maya-miller">Maya Miller</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/duaa-eldeib">Duaa Eldeib</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/max-blau">Max Blau</a>, photography by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/tony-luong">Tony Luong, special to ProPublica</a>, design by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/zisiga-mukulu">Zisiga Mukulu</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-08-25EDT07:00">Aug. 25, 7 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                            </div>
                    <div class="most-read-story">
                                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    


                    
    
        <div class="lead-art thumbnail">
            <a class="aspect-1-1" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/mental-health-wiltn-states">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271%27%20height%3D%271%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
                    srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/WITLN-States-Promo.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=105&amp;q=75&amp;w=105&amp;s=086b60a011fb28a5aca37383e438b8dd 105w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/WITLN-States-Promo.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=210&amp;q=75&amp;w=210&amp;s=9017007af4d2e065ea2a29097cf4e938 210w"
                    width="105"
                    height="105"
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/americas-mental-barrier">America’s Mental Barrier</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/mental-health-wiltn-states">
                                    What Mental Health Care Protections Exist in Your State?
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Insurers have wide latitude on when and how they can deny mental health care. We looked at the laws in all 50 states and found that some are charting new paths to secure mental health care access.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/annie-waldman">Annie Waldman</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/maya-miller">Maya Miller</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-08-27EDT07:00">Aug. 27, 7 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                            </div>
                    <div class="most-read-story">
                                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art thumbnail">
            <a class="aspect-1-1" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/school-closures-students-charter-schools-home-schooling-rochester">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271%27%20height%3D%271%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
                    srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Janice-Kpor_The-New-Yorker-_McFadden_20240808__00112_DSCF0636.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5034&amp;fp-y=0.2288&amp;h=105&amp;q=75&amp;w=105&amp;s=a14011ef061b6742f8fe69fd81ddf905 105w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/Janice-Kpor_The-New-Yorker-_McFadden_20240808__00112_DSCF0636.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5034&amp;fp-y=0.2288&amp;h=210&amp;q=75&amp;w=210&amp;s=0cc88375b645767bf7d1641a5cb34a7b 210w"
