    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/school-closures-students-charter-schools-home-schooling-rochester">
                                    The Unequal Effects of School Closings
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            As more families opt for charter and private schools or homeschooling in the wake of the pandemic, cities around the country are shuttering schools. The effects fall hardest on majority-Black schools and special-needs students.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/alec-macgillis">Alec MacGillis</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-08-26EDT05:00">Aug. 26, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
